Class OwnedBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.CMPUT3012019T02.alexandria.model.user.UserBook
      • ca.ualberta.CMPUT3012019T02.alexandria.model.user.OwnedBook

  • public class OwnedBook
extends UserBook
    This class represents a relationship between a User and a Book, where the User has ownership of a particular Book. It also contains specific data that a User can attach to a Book they own.
